@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.59
    v0 = (0.93 / ((v2 + 0.98 / v0 + 0.10) / wp.exp(v0 + 0.94)))
    v2 = (0.58 - (0.85 - tmp))
    v2 = (0.09 + wp.abs(v2))
